 we are now my project is to bring this new picture together a key question in the new big history is what has brought us to where we are today a fascination of big history is the question of origins so the focus of my work is the questions of origin that have been the heart of our understanding of human history for over two centuries what are the origins of biologically modern humans our species homo sapiens what are the origins of agriculture the break with hunter gatherer societies what are the origins of civilization and city life what are the origins of the modern industrial world i think that the archaeological answers to these questions will surprise many people edit this page attach file add image references print page last modified sun feb 26 2012 02 38 you must signin to post comments group admin versions track changes site home michael shanks origins
